title: Case Was Received
body: On March 1, 2021, we received your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190120000, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
